        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[DBIx::Class vs DBIO]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[I took a moment off writing the book on DBIx::Class to explore DBIO, a new competitor in the Perl ORM sector. I faced some difficulties installing the system but shared useful comparisons of standard table schemas, result classes, and test cases demonstrating the similarity.]]></description>
