        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[SQL JOIN using DBIx::Class]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[ In this post, I share the application of different SQL JOINs within the database application created using DBIx::Class. It illustrates the four important types of joins using an example of unit testing which employs User and Profile tables.]]></description>
