        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Flatpak with Perl]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[In this tutorial, I show how to effectively use Flatpak to containerise their Perl script in a sandbox that is isolated from the network. Using a manifest file that pulls in dependencies from CPAN, I explain how to compile and run their Perl application across all possible modern Linux distributions without running into any trouble.]]></description>
            <pubDate>2026.07.07</pubDate>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://theweeklychallenge.org/blog/flatpak-with-perl/</guid>
            <link>https://theweeklychallenge.org/blog/flatpak-with-perl/</link>
            
            
            
            <author><![CDATA[mohammad_anwar]]></author>
            
                
            
            
        </item>
        
